# Service Boundaries

- Keep deployable service boundaries explicit even though code lives in one repo.
- Do not import across services directly; use typed contracts, generated clients, queues, or documented APIs.
- `backend-facade` is the product API surface for web, Mac, and Windows apps.
- Do not put AI orchestration logic in `backend-facade`.
- Do not put tenant auth ownership, billing/admin state, or product persistence in `services/ai-backend`.
- Add or update a service-boundary doc before creating a new service or shared package.

